NK013(pa)010:0: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba 'bring po'i dbang gi
NK013(pa)010:1: cho ga dkyil 'khor rgya mtshor 'jug pa'i gru chen
NK013(pa)010:3: sgyu 'phrul dra ba zhi ba 'bring po'i dbang gi
NK013(pa)010:4: cho ga dkyil 'khor rgya mtshor 'jug pa'i gru chen
NK013(pa)010:5: zhes bya ba / bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)010:6: rang rig ye shes gnyis 'dzin 'khrul rtog gis /
NK013(pa)010:8: / 'ching ba kun grol mi 'gyur bde chen nyid //
NK013(pa)010:9: bla meda sku bzhi'i rdo rjer byang chub pa //
NK013(pa)010:10: drin can bla ma'i zhabs zung gtsug gis mchod //
NK013(pa)010:11: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi gshegs pa'i shul //
NK013(pa)010:12: gsang chen snying po'i de nyid nges pa'i don //
NK013(pa)010:13: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK013(pa)010:14: skal ldan gzhug thabs dbang bskur cho ga bri //
NK013(pa)010:15: de la 'dir he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK013(pa)010:16: dang po sa yi cho ga ste /
NK013(pa)010:17: gnyis pa la ni sta gon gnas //
NK013(pa)010:18: gsum pa 'jug pa'i cho ga bya //
NK013(pa)010:19: zhes gsungs pa ltar las nub dang po sa'i cho ga dang /
NK013(pa)010:20: gnyis pa sta gon gyi cho ga gzhan rnams rje
NK013(pa)010:21: bla mas mdzad pa'i dkyil chog rdo rje'i phreng ba
NK013(pa)010:22: ltar bya zhing / 'dir slob ma lhag par gnas
NK013(pa)010:23: pa'i cho ga ni dkyil 'khor gyi shar lhor man+dala
NK013(pa)010:24: khru gang ba la 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa bri
NK013(pa)010:25: ltar bya zhing / / slob dpon gyi drung du
NK013(pa)010:26: so shing sogs 'og tu dgos pa'i yo byad thams
NK013(pa)010:28: de nas slob bu rnams khrus bya /
NK013(pa)010:30: srung 'khor bsgom rjes chos bshad thun mong ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)010:32: 'di ni sde snod dang rgyud thams cad kyi rtsa
NK013(pa)010:33: ba'am 'phro gzhi lta bur gyur pa dpal sgyu 'phrul
NK013(pa)010:34: d+r+wa ba chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs te /
NK013(pa)010:35: de la'ang smin grol gyi rim pa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK013(pa)010:36: 'dir smin byed kyi dbang nyid bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin zhing /
NK013(pa)010:37: dbang de la'ang sbyor dngos rjes gsum las /
NK013(pa)010:38: skabs 'dir sbyor ba sta gon gyi bye brag slob
NK013(pa)010:39: ma lhag par gnas pa'i chos rnams sgrub par byed
NK013(pa)010:40: pa yin pas / de'i slad du thog mar khyed
NK013(pa)010:41: rang rnams kyi lus longs spyod dus gsum dang 'brel
NK013(pa)010:42: ba'i dge tshogs rgya mtsho dang bcas pa thams cad
NK013(pa)010:43: gcig tu bsdoms nas 'bul ba'i mos 'dun bgyis te
NK013(pa)010:46: de nas slob ma rnams kyis sems bskyed par bya ste /
NK013(pa)010:47: de la'ang gnyis las dang po kun rdzob byang chub
NK013(pa)010:48: kyi sems bskyed pa'i don du 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod
NK013(pa)010:49: / bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK013(pa)010:50: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK013(pa)010:51: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK013(pa)010:52: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK013(pa)010:54: gnyis pa don dam byang chub tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:55: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)010:56: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)010:57: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK013(pa)010:58: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK013(pa)010:59: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)010:60: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK013(pa)010:65: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)010:66: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)010:67: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK013(pa)010:68: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK013(pa)010:69: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)010:70: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)010:71: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK013(pa)010:72: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK013(pa)010:73: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)010:74: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK013(pa)010:80: de'i lan du slob dpon gyis /
NK013(pa)010:81: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las //
NK013(pa)010:82: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK013(pa)010:83: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK013(pa)010:84: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK013(pa)010:85: bdag dang bdag gis so sor 'dzin //
NK013(pa)010:86: sus kyang ma bcings bcings med de //
NK013(pa)010:87: bcing bar bya ba yod ma yin //
NK013(pa)010:88: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis //
NK013(pa)010:89: nan gyis mkha' la mdud pa dor //
NK013(pa)010:90: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK013(pa)010:91: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK013(pa)010:92: khyod la rab tu bstan par bya //
NK013(pa)010:94: skabs 'dir dkyil 'khor gyi don bshad la nges shes bskyed par bya ste /
NK013(pa)010:96: dkyil 'khor don dang yon tan rnams //
NK013(pa)010:97: gsal byas rab tu brod pa bskyed //
NK013(pa)010:100: gsang ba sgyu 'phrul pa'i lugs kyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK013(pa)010:106: bkod pa lha'i 'khor lor rdzogs par snang ba'o //
NK013(pa)010:108: man+da la'i sgra las drangs na snying po 'dzin pa'am snying po len pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:109: zlum po'am bskor ba'i don gyis dkyil 'khor ro //
NK013(pa)010:111: tshogs gnyis rdzogs par byed pa'o //
NK013(pa)010:114: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK013(pa)010:116: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK013(pa)010:118: 'dir 'jug bya'i dkyil 'khor ni lhag pa gzugs brnyan te /
NK013(pa)010:119: 'di lta bu'i gsang sngags bla na med pa'i dkyil
NK013(pa)010:120: 'khor 'di 'dra mthong ba tsam gyis kyang bskal pa
NK013(pa)010:121: bye ba du mar bsags pa'i sdig sgrib 'dag pa
NK013(pa)010:122: sogs phan yon dang ldan na zhugs shing dbang bskur
NK013(pa)010:123: bas ni lta ci smos te de'i phyir dga' spro
NK013(pa)010:124: yang dag par bskyed mdzod cig /
NK013(pa)010:126: de nas slob mas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:127: rdor sems gtso bo khyod la 'dud //
NK013(pa)010:128: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod do //
NK013(pa)010:129: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK013(pa)010:130: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song ste //
NK013(pa)010:131: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK013(pa)010:132: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK013(pa)010:134: de nas gnang ba sbyin cing drang ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:135: lag gi rdo rje la 'jur bcug ste /
NK013(pa)010:136: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde bar //
NK013(pa)010:137: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK013(pa)010:138: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung //
NK013(pa)010:139: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK013(pa)010:140: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK013(pa)010:141: ser sna spangs pa'i ngang yid kyis //
NK013(pa)010:142: gtong zhing rang sems brtan por zung //
NK013(pa)010:143: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rdzogs dbang byin //
NK013(pa)010:145: khyad par can gyi don la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:146: bdag ni las mchog skal bar ldan //
NK013(pa)010:147: deng nas theg pa chen po la //
NK013(pa)010:148: brtan par bya phyir bdag la ni //
NK013(pa)010:149: ye shes bsrung ba mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)010:151: de nas bgegs bskrad cing sgrib pa phral ba la /
NK013(pa)010:155: tshe mi yar bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK013(pa)010:156: dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i sa bon las yi ge b+h+r+aum re slob ma'i dpral bar spros /
NK013(pa)010:159: dung khang du zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang
NK013(pa)010:160: gnas sgo gcig pa sgo khyud can gcig tu gyur
NK013(pa)010:161: / de'i nang du h'u yig gsal ba las h'u
NK013(pa)010:162: zhes brjod pas slob ma'i tshe'i dngos po thams cad
NK013(pa)010:163: / h'u la bsdu / badz+ra h'u k+aa ra h'u phata /
NK013(pa)010:165: h'u k+aa ra sngon po tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:166: zla gam gyi gnam sgo la /
NK013(pa)010:167: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u phata /
NK013(pa)010:169: khro bo mi g.yo ba ljang nag ral gri dang sdigs mdzub can gcig gis sgo bsrung bar gyur /
NK013(pa)010:170: gnyis pa la bgegs bskrad pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:171: sgrib pa phral ba gnyis kyi /
NK013(pa)010:173: slob dpon zhe sdang rdo rjer gsal bas /
NK013(pa)010:174: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK013(pa)010:175: ha la ha la ha la h'u /
NK013(pa)010:177: sprul pa'i khro tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa spros /
NK013(pa)010:178: bdud bgegs log par 'dren pa'i tshogs thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:180: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)010:181: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:182: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:183: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:184: khyad par du'ang bcom ldan 'das sgyu 'phrul zhi khro
NK013(pa)010:185: rnam par rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams
NK013(pa)010:187: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis rlabs kyis /
NK013(pa)010:188: zhes bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)010:189: 'dir 'dus pa'i slob bu rnams la gnod cing 'tshe
NK013(pa)010:190: ba'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par dengs
NK013(pa)010:192: h'u bzhi pa'i sngags lan gsum brjod cing gu gul gyis bdug /
NK013(pa)010:195: slob dpon gyi lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga
NK013(pa)010:196: la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du h'u
NK013(pa)010:197: s+w+aa +aam h+aam / g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la
NK013(pa)010:198: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du m+aum l+aam
NK013(pa)010:199: m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan pa rnams rigs lnga
NK013(pa)010:200: yab yum bcur gyur par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:206: zhes phyag rgya bsdams pas rigs lnga yab yum mnyam par sbyor bar bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:207: gong ltar bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)010:208: slob bu 'di rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:209: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:211: lta ba dman pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:212: chos kyis phongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:213: bag chags ngan pa'i sgrib pa la sogs te sgrib
NK013(pa)010:214: pa'i phung po ji snyed pa thams cad phyag rgya'i
NK013(pa)010:217: zhes pa'i sngags mang du brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs pas /
NK013(pa)010:218: rigs lnga'i sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK013(pa)010:219: zer 'phros pas slob bu'i sgrib pa mtha' dag bsregs
NK013(pa)010:220: shing sbyangs / dung khang gi khro bo gnyis kyang
NK013(pa)010:221: zhu lugs su thim pa'i rkyen gyis bu'i lus kyang
NK013(pa)010:222: 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung gser zhun ma lta
NK013(pa)010:224: de nas slob bu lhar bskyed pa la bskur brlab go bgo lus bsrung bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:225: h'u zhes brjod pas de nyid h'u yig dkar po gcig tu gyur /
NK013(pa)010:228: 'phro 'dus rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur /
NK013(pa)010:232: rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po rdor dril
NK013(pa)010:233: 'dzin pa rgyan dang cha lugs thams cad rdzogs par
NK013(pa)010:234: bsam / so so'i phyag rgya slob ma'i mgo'i gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:235: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:240: kri t+y+aa nush+th+aa na zhes bcug pas dbang bskur /
NK013(pa)010:241: +aahmh'u zhes brjod cing rdo rje gnas gsum du gtugs pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK013(pa)010:242: slar yang rdo rje rtse lnga'i rgya bcings pas gnas gsum du bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:243: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:247: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su dpral bar sku rdo
NK013(pa)010:248: rje rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa
NK013(pa)010:249: 'dzin pa / mgrin par gsung rdo rje snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma +aahs mtshan pa 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)010:250: snying gar thugs rdo rje mi bskyod pa mthing ga
NK013(pa)010:251: rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa 'dzin pa rnams kyis
NK013(pa)010:253: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya spyi bor bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:254: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK013(pa)010:256: mdzub mo g.yas su trum las khro bo rdo rje
NK013(pa)010:257: gnod sbyin nag po phyag gnyis kyis mche ba dang
NK013(pa)010:258: sdigs mdzub / g.yon du las khro bo mi 'chi
NK013(pa)010:259: thab sbyor dmar po rgya gram dang sdigs mdzub can
NK013(pa)010:260: sdigs mdzub / du bskyed la / trum /
NK013(pa)010:265: spyi bo rnams su rim par mdzub mo gnyis bsnol ba reg pas /
NK013(pa)010:266: gnas de dang der khro bo gnyis po zung re
NK013(pa)010:267: zhabs bsnol nas zhal phyir gzigs te bsrung ba'i las
NK013(pa)010:268: mdzad pa'i thugs ka nas rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK013(pa)010:269: byung bas bsrungs shing brtan par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)010:270: de nas so shing dor ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:271: so shing sor bcu gnyis pa dri bzang gis byugs
NK013(pa)010:272: shing rtse mor me tog gi phreng ba bcings pa
NK013(pa)010:273: slob ma rnams kyi dngos grub kyi ltas brtag pa'i
NK013(pa)010:274: nus pa dang ldan par bsam la sbyin zhing /
NK013(pa)010:275: des kyang mkha' dbyings kyi rgyas bzung la sos 'cha'
NK013(pa)010:276: zhing drud pa ltar byas pas sdig sgrib thams cad
NK013(pa)010:279: zhes man+dala gyi steng du dor bas tshugs na bzang /
NK013(pa)010:281: mtshams bzhir dngos grub dman pa 'grub par bstan /
NK013(pa)010:282: de nas khyor chu blud pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:286: rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin gyi chu'i rdul phra
NK013(pa)010:287: rab tu zhu bas rmi lam gsal bar byed pa'i
NK013(pa)010:288: nus pa dang ldan par bsam zhing khyor bar blugs
NK013(pa)010:289: la / sarba sam sho d+ha na ye h'u phata /
NK013(pa)010:290: ces brjod cing 'thung du bcug nas lhag mas kha lag bkru /
NK013(pa)010:291: de nas srung skud 'ching ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:292: srung skud dmar po sum sgril la /
NK013(pa)010:293: big+h+n+aam ta krita a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK013(pa)010:294: ces brjod cing mdud pa gsum btab pas /
NK013(pa)010:295: bar chad bsrung ba'i nus pa dang ldan par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:296: sngags des pho'i dpung pa g.yon dang mo'i g.yas 'ching
NK013(pa)010:297: zhing mdud pa'i steng du srin lag gis dri'i thig
NK013(pa)010:298: le byas la rgya gram du reg pas bsrung bar
NK013(pa)010:299: bsam mo // de nas ku sha byin pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:300: ku sha'i chun po che chung gnyis /
NK013(pa)010:301: rmi lam mi 'khrug pa'i nus pa dang ldan par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:303: zhes sngas dang stan gyi don du byin /
NK013(pa)010:304: de'i rjes su dngos grub kyi snod skyon ngo shes
NK013(pa)010:305: pa'i ched du dbang gi gegs brgyad bshad par bya
NK013(pa)010:306: ste / sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos grub mchog /
NK013(pa)010:307: dbang dang byin rlabs 'byung ba ni //
NK013(pa)010:308: dper na dwangs pa'i rgya mtsho la //
NK013(pa)010:311: byin rlabs dbang mchog thob pa'i gegs //
NK013(pa)010:312: rnam pa brgyad du rgyal bas bshad //
NK013(pa)010:313: ston pa sngon byung slob dpon la //
NK013(pa)010:314: bka' gcog brnyas par byed pa ni //
NK013(pa)010:315: dbang dang dngos grub dang po'i gegs //
NK013(pa)010:316: bla med 'gro ba'i rdo rje spun /
NK013(pa)010:318: / 'khu ldog gdung ba'i sems med na //
NK013(pa)010:319: dbang dang dngos grub gnyis pa'i gegs //
NK013(pa)010:320: byang chub sems la 'dud med cing //
NK013(pa)010:321: thar lam 'dren pa'i lha spong ba //
NK013(pa)010:322: dbang dang byin rlabs gsum pa'i gegs //
NK013(pa)010:323: snying rje'i yul gyur sems can la //
NK013(pa)010:324: thag pa gcod pa bzhi pa'i gegs //
NK013(pa)010:325: gsang bas gsang ba'i lta spyod rnams //
NK013(pa)010:326: yongs la 'byin pa gegs lnga yin //
NK013(pa)010:327: thar lam ston la 'dud med cing //
NK013(pa)010:328: ser snas bcings pa drug pa'i gegs //
NK013(pa)010:329: gzu lum dbang byed las la spyod //
NK013(pa)010:330: dngos grub myur ba'i gegs bdun pa /
NK013(pa)010:332: / 'dod pa'i khe grags lhur len zhing //
NK013(pa)010:333: gsang ba'i dam tshig spong ba ste /
NK013(pa)010:335: / 'di ni brgyad pa'i gegs su bstan //
NK013(pa)010:336: nyes pa 'di dag spong ba ni //
NK013(pa)010:337: dngos grub dbang gi snod du 'gyur //
NK013(pa)010:338: bu kye nang par 'dri byed pas //
NK013(pa)010:339: dkyil 'khor steng du legs par nyol //
NK013(pa)010:340: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha sa ma ya dan+da h'u /
NK013(pa)010:341: zhes las bum gyi chus gtor nas /
NK013(pa)010:342: do nub seng ge nyal thabs kyis bde bar nyol la /
NK013(pa)010:343: mtshan mo'i thun gsum pa tho rengs kyi dus rmi
NK013(pa)010:344: lam bzang ngan gang rmis pa de nang par bdag
NK013(pa)010:346: slob bu rmi lam ngan la rmis pa rnams rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags /
NK013(pa)010:347: badz+rak+sha h'u zhes pa dang mche ba'i phyag rgyas bsrung /
NK013(pa)010:348: kun rmi lam ngan na drag po'i sbyin sreg sogs kyang bya'o //
NK013(pa)010:349: de la rmi lam bzang ngan gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK013(pa)010:350: khrus byed pa sku gsung thugs rten mthong ba la sogs pa rmis na bzang /
NK013(pa)010:351: thur du 'babs pa la sogs pa mthong na ngan no //
NK013(pa)010:352: de dag ni slob ma lhag par gnas pa'i cho ga'o //
NK013(pa)010:353: de ltar sa chog dang sta gon gyi rim pa rnams song nas /
NK013(pa)010:357: sgrub mchod rnams rje bla mas mdzad pa'i dkyil chog rin chen phreng ba dang /
NK013(pa)010:358: sgrub thabs ye shes char 'bebs ltar bya'o /
NK013(pa)010:361: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga dang /
NK013(pa)010:362: zhugs pa la mngon par dbang bskur ba'i cho ga gnyis /
NK013(pa)010:365: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK013(pa)010:366: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul ba //
NK013(pa)010:367: bgegs bskrad lhar rlob dam tshig sbyin //
NK013(pa)010:368: de nyid dbab dang chu nan dang //
NK013(pa)010:369: bsgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK013(pa)010:370: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK013(pa)010:371: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK013(pa)010:372: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad /
NK013(pa)010:375: zhes chos bco brgyad du yod pa las /
NK013(pa)010:376: dang po slob dpon 'jug pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:377: dkyil 'khor bzhengs sgrub kyi las rim kun tshar ba dang /
NK013(pa)010:378: slob dpon rang nyid slob ma 'jug pa ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs te /
NK013(pa)010:379: dbang rnams bdag 'jug gi tshul du blang ba'am /
NK013(pa)010:380: mi nus na dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor gus pas 'dug ste /
NK013(pa)010:381: rig pa'i me tog dor nas dngos grub skul ba sgrub thabs ltar byas pas 'grub bo //
NK013(pa)010:382: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug par bzod gsol gnang ba zhu ba ni //
NK013(pa)010:383: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK013(pa)010:384: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)010:386: bdag gis slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK013(pa)010:387: zhes gsol bas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams 'dzum pa'i
NK013(pa)010:388: mdangs kyis slob bu dkyil 'khor du chug la dbang
NK013(pa)010:389: bco brgyad snod dang 'tshams par bskur cig /
NK013(pa)010:390: ces gnang ba thob par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)010:391: gsum pa khrus bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:393: ji ltar bltams pa sogs kyis las bum chus khrus byas nas /
NK013(pa)010:394: mtshams gcod srung 'khor sgom pa sngon du 'gro bas chos bshad par bya ste /
NK013(pa)010:396: 'o nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK013(pa)010:397: kyi don du bla na med pa yang dag par
NK013(pa)010:398: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi slob pa'i zung 'jug sku
NK013(pa)010:399: bzhi ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid chen po gang gi
NK013(pa)010:400: go 'phang tshe 'di nyid la mngon du bsgrub par
NK013(pa)010:401: bya / de'i ched du gsang sngags rdo rje theg
NK013(pa)010:402: pa'i lam gyi 'jug sgo dang po smin byed dbang
NK013(pa)010:403: gi rim pa rnams legs par nod nas lam zab
NK013(pa)010:404: mo bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa gnyis la tshul bzhin
NK013(pa)010:405: du bslab par bagyi'o snyam pa'i byang chub mchog tu
NK013(pa)010:406: sems bskyed pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)010:407: chos nyan pa'i kun tu spyod pa rnams kyang blang dor ma 'dzol bar bgyis te /
NK013(pa)010:409: de la gang zhig gsan par bya ba'i chos kyi
NK013(pa)010:410: rnam grangs kyang spyir bdag cag gi ston pa thabs
NK013(pa)010:411: la mkhas shing thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa
NK013(pa)010:412: de nyid kyis gdul bya'i sems can rnams kyi khams
NK013(pa)010:414: bsam pa'i rjes su 'gro ba'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK013(pa)010:415: dpag tu med pa zhig bskor bar mdzad pa yang
NK013(pa)010:416: yin / re zhig spang gnyen gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK013(pa)010:417: gdul bya'i rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa'i bye brag brgyad
NK013(pa)010:418: khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por chos kyi phung po'ang
NK013(pa)010:419: de snyed cig tu grangs nges pa yin te /
NK013(pa)010:421: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK013(pa)010:422: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:424: / 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK013(pa)010:425: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK013(pa)010:426: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK013(pa)010:427: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK013(pa)010:428: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK013(pa)010:429: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK013(pa)010:430: sde snod bzhi ba nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK013(pa)010:431: mdor na brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa kun //
NK013(pa)010:432: nyon mongs 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs par zad //
NK013(pa)010:434: de yang gzhung dang man ngag tsam gyi sgo nas bsdu na //
NK013(pa)010:435: gzhung mtshan nyid phar phyin gyi theg pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:436: man ngag gsang chen rdo rje'i theg pa gnyis su 'du ba yin te /
NK013(pa)010:438: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK013(pa)010:439: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:445: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK013(pa)010:446: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK013(pa)010:447: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas nas //
NK013(pa)010:448: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK013(pa)010:449: zhes bshad pa ltar khyad chos bzhi'i sgo nas khyad
NK013(pa)010:450: par du 'phags pa gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa
NK013(pa)010:451: nyid yin zhing / de la'ang shes byed rgyud sde'i
NK013(pa)010:452: rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig yod kyang
NK013(pa)010:453: lta spyod tsam gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK013(pa)010:454: spyod pa gtso bor ston pa bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK013(pa)010:455: lta ba gtso bor ston pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud
NK013(pa)010:456: de gnyis su gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha' dag
NK013(pa)010:458: der yang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud tsam dang /
NK013(pa)010:459: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud gnyis su yod pa las /
NK013(pa)010:460: 'di ni rnal 'byor bla na med pa la nang
NK013(pa)010:461: gses bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum ston pa'i gzhung rgyud
NK013(pa)010:462: lung man ngag gsum yod pa'i dang po rgyud ma
NK013(pa)010:463: h+aa yo ga / de la'ang bskyed rim thabs kyi
NK013(pa)010:464: cha dang rdzogs rim rlung gtso bor byed pas gsal
NK013(pa)010:465: stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis nyams su
NK013(pa)010:466: len pa ma h+aa'i ma h+aa ste pha rgyud gsang
NK013(pa)010:467: ba 'dus pa la sogs pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:468: bskyed rim gyi spros pa shas chung zhing shes rab
NK013(pa)010:469: bardzogasa pa'i rim pa khams byang chub kyi sems thig
NK013(pa)010:470: le gtso bor byed pas bde stong rnam par mi
NK013(pa)010:471: rtog pa'i tshul du nyams su len pa ma h+aa'i
NK013(pa)010:472: a nu ste ma rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang
NK013(pa)010:473: dpal yang dag la sogs pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:474: bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug cing de'ang rdzogs rim rtsa
NK013(pa)010:475: thig rlung gsum las bskyed pa'i bde gsal rnam par
NK013(pa)010:476: mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK013(pa)010:477: khyad par 'od gsal ye shes chen po la gtso
NK013(pa)010:478: bor byed pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len pa ma
NK013(pa)010:479: h+aa'i a ti ste gnyis med kyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul
NK013(pa)010:480: d+r+wa ba la sogs pa las /
NK013(pa)010:481: 'dir snga 'gyur bka' ma'i bka' srol rdo rje sems
NK013(pa)010:482: dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK013(pa)010:483: dbang bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin /
NK013(pa)010:484: de la'ang thog mar nges shes 'dren pa bla ma brgyud pa'i lo rgyus kyi dbang du byas na /
NK013(pa)010:486: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK013(pa)010:487: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK013(pa)010:488: ces gsungs pa ltar gsum las /
NK013(pa)010:489: dang po phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad
NK013(pa)010:490: kyi bdag nyid ston pa rigs drug pa bcom ldan
NK013(pa)010:493: 'chad pa'i skyes bu de bzhin gshegs pa lnga yang mngon par snang bar mdzad nas /
NK013(pa)010:494: rdo rje gsang ba la sogs pa rig pa khyad
NK013(pa)010:495: par can gyi 'khor rnams la rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK013(pa)010:496: nyid dgongs pa brda'i gsung gis /
NK013(pa)010:497: dus rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor bstan pa ni rgyal ba dgongs brgyud do //
NK013(pa)010:498: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor rnams kyi nang nas rigs
NK013(pa)010:499: gsum mgon pos lha klu gnod sbyin gyi gnas su
NK013(pa)010:501: thub pa'i dbang po mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK013(pa)010:502: lang+ka'i yul te sing ga la'i gling gi ri bo
NK013(pa)010:503: ma la ya'am deng sang su ma na k+au ta'i
NK013(pa)010:504: ri zhes grags pa'i rtse mor gsang bdag gis lha
NK013(pa)010:507: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK013(pa)010:509: mi las skal ldan li tsa bi dri med grags pa ste /
NK013(pa)010:510: dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga la bshad pa rnams ni rig 'dzin brda brgyud do //
NK013(pa)010:511: de nas gang zag snyan brgyud ni /
NK013(pa)010:512: gsang bdag gis rigs can lnga la chos 'khor bskor
NK013(pa)010:513: ba'i byin rlabs kyis za hor gyi rgyal po dzahl
NK013(pa)010:514: rmi ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun rmis shing de'i rjes
NK013(pa)010:516: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK013(pa)010:517: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK013(pa)010:518: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK013(pa)010:519: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK013(pa)010:520: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK013(pa)010:521: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK013(pa)010:522: bsod nams chen po'i mthus snang ba'i //
NK013(pa)010:523: gsang ba'i bdag pos snang bar 'gyur //
NK013(pa)010:524: zhes lung bstan pa ltar rgyal po nyid kyi pho
NK013(pa)010:525: brang gi khang thog tu tan+t+ra chen po sde bco
NK013(pa)010:526: brgyad kyi glegs bam char du babs shing /
NK013(pa)010:527: gsang ba'i bdag pos dngos su byin gyis brlabs nas don gyi brgyud pa gtad de /
NK013(pa)010:528: tshig gi brgyud pa li tsa bi nas len par
NK013(pa)010:529: rjes su gnang bzhin slar yang de nyid nas legs
NK013(pa)010:532: gsang ba'i bdag po nas li tsa bi dri med grags pa /
NK013(pa)010:533: rgyal po dzah ku ku r+aa dzah in+d+ra b+hu ti /
NK013(pa)010:534: u pa r+aa dzah sras mo go ma de wi rnams la rim par brgyud de /
NK013(pa)010:535: thams cad tshogs kyi spyod pa'i nye rgyu la brten
NK013(pa)010:536: nas rang rang gi tshom bu dang bcas te rdo
NK013(pa)010:537: rje 'chang chen po'i sa la mngon du gshegs pa
NK013(pa)010:538: sha stag go // sras mos sgeg pa rdo rje dang slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK013(pa)010:539: de gnyis kas pan chen bi ma la mi tra /
NK013(pa)010:540: des bod du lo ts+aa ba rma gnyags gnyis /
NK013(pa)010:541: rma rin chen mchog nas mkhas pa gtsug gyer rnam gnyis /
NK013(pa)010:543: gnyags lo ye shes gzhon nu nas sog po dpal ye la brgyud de /
NK013(pa)010:544: zhang dang sog pos gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes la bskur /
NK013(pa)010:545: de nas gnubs yon tan rgya mtsho yab sras dang /
NK013(pa)010:546: chos lung gi nyang khu dbon nas lha rje zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas /
NK013(pa)010:547: de'i slob ma rtse mo bzhi las lta sgom gyi rtse mo zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK013(pa)010:548: de'i slob ma ka ba bzhi dang glan sh+aaka byang las /
NK013(pa)010:549: gsang bdag chen po sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge
NK013(pa)010:550: sogs nas 'og min o rgyan smin grol gling gi
NK013(pa)010:551: rje gter chen bla ma yab sras nas rim par
NK013(pa)010:552: brgyud de / kho bo cag gi bla ma dam
NK013(pa)010:553: pa bka' drin mnyam med dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i dbang
NK013(pa)010:554: phyug khyab bdag 'khor lo'i mgon po mtshan brjod par
NK013(pa)010:555: dka' ba 'di zhes pa'i zhal snga nas bdag rgyud
NK013(pa)010:556: dbang gi chu bos smin par mdzad pa yin /
NK013(pa)010:557: brgyud pa de las byung ba'i chos de la'ang /
NK013(pa)010:558: lam gyi gzhi smin byed dbang gi rim pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:559: de'i nyams len grol byed bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa
NK013(pa)010:560: gnyis su yod pa las 'dir dbang bskur ba'i rim
NK013(pa)010:561: pa de skabs su bab pa yin /
NK013(pa)010:562: de la dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK013(pa)010:563: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi tshogs pa la brten nas go 'phang gi chos rgyud la 'jog pa'i las kyis /
NK013(pa)010:564: rgyud kyi dri ma byang ba'am nyams smad par byas shing /
NK013(pa)010:565: thar pa'i myu gu mngon du skyes pa'am /
NK013(pa)010:566: skye nges kyi sa bon khyad par can gsos thebs
NK013(pa)010:567: pas lam bsgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi
NK013(pa)010:568: nus pa mthu can du smin par byas pa ste
NK013(pa)010:569: / sa bon gsos thebs pa'i cha de sngags kyi sdom pa'ang yin la /
NK013(pa)010:572: a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK013(pa)010:573: mngon par gtor bas na dbang ste /
NK013(pa)010:574: sbyang bya sgo gsum gyi dri ma gtor zhing 'khrud par byed pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)010:575: yang mngon par blugs pas na dbang ste /
NK013(pa)010:576: lam sgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi nus pa khyad par can rgyud la 'jog pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)010:577: de ltar yang brtag gnyis las /
NK013(pa)010:578: gtor dang blugs pa zhes bya ba //
NK013(pa)010:579: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya //
NK013(pa)010:581: dbye na dad pa can rjes su 'dzin pa la phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK013(pa)010:582: brtson 'grus can rjes su 'dzin pa la nus pa'i dbang lnga /
NK013(pa)010:583: brtul zhugs can rjes su 'dzin pa la zab mo'i dbang gsum gsungs te /
NK013(pa)010:585: dad dang brtson 'grus brtul zhugs la //
NK013(pa)010:586: phan dang nus pa'i dbang bskur bya //
NK013(pa)010:587: shes rab dbang bskur rim par bcas //
NK013(pa)010:588: brtse bas chud mi za bar sbyin //
NK013(pa)010:590: de yang dbang bskur ba ni dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin la /
NK013(pa)010:591: de la'ang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK013(pa)010:592: sems can shin tu gdul dka' gang //
NK013(pa)010:593: sdo ma pa 'dzin par mi byed cing //
NK013(pa)010:594: dad dang ldan pa med pa yang /
NK013(pa)010:596: / 'jug pa nyid ni dgag mi bya //
NK013(pa)010:597: zhes pas re zhig dbang gi snod du ma gyur pa'i gang zag yin na'ang /
NK013(pa)010:598: dkyil 'khor du bcug pa tsam la 'gal ba med par gsungs mod /
NK013(pa)010:599: dkyil 'khor du ma bcug pa la dbang bskur ba ni nam du'ang mi rung ste /
NK013(pa)010:601: dkyil 'khor ma mthong ba rnams kyi mdun du ma smra zhig ces gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)010:603: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK013(pa)010:604: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK013(pa)010:605: zhes gsungs pa ltar sta gon du gnas pa yan chad song nas /
NK013(pa)010:607: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bya ba dang /
NK013(pa)010:608: rdo rje slob ma'i bya ba gnyis yod pa las /
NK013(pa)010:609: slob dpon gyi bgyi 'os dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa /
NK013(pa)010:611: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du rig pas 'jug pa rnams chad lhag med par sngon du grub /
NK013(pa)010:612: da khyed rang slob ma rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK013(pa)010:613: lha dang skal ba mnyam pa'i ched du dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos dang /
NK013(pa)010:614: zhugs nas dbang nod pa'i bya ba gnyis las /
NK013(pa)010:615: 'dir 'jug pa'i yan lag khrus dang bgegs bsal ba sngon du song nas /
NK013(pa)010:616: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo tha mi
NK013(pa)010:617: dad pa la dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos rnams
NK013(pa)010:618: zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod /
NK013(pa)010:620: bzhi pa gdong dgab pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:621: dar ram ras dmar po'i mig dar /
NK013(pa)010:623: +aa kham w+ai ra h'u gis me tog gtad pa snyim par thogs pas thal mo sbyar la /
NK013(pa)010:624: rdor sems gtso bo khyod la 'dud //
NK013(pa)010:625: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK013(pa)010:626: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK013(pa)010:627: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song ste //
NK013(pa)010:628: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK013(pa)010:629: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK013(pa)010:630: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK013(pa)010:633: bu khyod ci la dga' zhes dri /
NK013(pa)010:635: skal ba bzang la bdag daga'o //
NK013(pa)010:637: de nas lag gi rdo rje phyed byin la /
NK013(pa)010:638: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde bar //
NK013(pa)010:639: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK013(pa)010:640: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje zung //
NK013(pa)010:641: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK013(pa)010:642: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK013(pa)010:643: ser sna spangs pa'i dang yid kyis //
NK013(pa)010:644: gtong zhing rang sems brtan por zung //
NK013(pa)010:645: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK013(pa)010:646: zhes rang gi mdun du drangs /
NK013(pa)010:647: skabs 'dir dkyil 'khor gyi yol ba bsal /
NK013(pa)010:648: drug pa lus dbul ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:649: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK013(pa)010:650: yon tan phrin las kyi ye shes thob par bya
NK013(pa)010:651: ba'i phyir 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rtogs pa mngon du
NK013(pa)010:652: gyur pa rnams la lus phul bar bsam la thal
NK013(pa)010:654: sarba bud+d+ha p+au dzo ba s+th+aa n+aa ya +aat+ma nam nir+y+aa ta y+aa mi /
NK013(pa)010:655: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye shes thob pa'i snod
NK013(pa)010:656: rung du bya ba'i phyir da ltar gyi sangs rgyas
NK013(pa)010:657: bla ma rnams la lus phul bar bsam la thal
NK013(pa)010:658: mo smin mtshams su sbyar te /
NK013(pa)010:659: +aa tsar+ya p+au dza ba s+th+aa n+aa ya +aat+ma nam nir+y+aa ta y+aa mi /
NK013(pa)010:660: sems can thams cad kyi don mi 'dor zhing mthar
NK013(pa)010:661: phyin par bya ba'i phyir ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK013(pa)010:662: sems can thams cad la lus phul bar bsam thal
NK013(pa)010:664: ba ke la sa t+wa pu tso ba s+th+aa n+aa ya +aat+ma nam nir+y+aa ta y+aa mi /
NK013(pa)010:666: bdun pa bgegs bskrad pa la sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK013(pa)010:669: tshe mi yar bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK013(pa)010:670: dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i sa bon las yi ge b+h+r+aum re slob ma'i dpral bar spros /
NK013(pa)010:673: dung khang du zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang
NK013(pa)010:674: gnam sgo gcig pa sgo khyud can gcig tu gyur
NK013(pa)010:675: / de'i nang du h+aum yig gsal ba las h'u
NK013(pa)010:676: zhes brjod pas slob ma'i tshe'i 'di dngos po thams
NK013(pa)010:678: badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)010:680: h+aum k+aa ra sngon po tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:681: zla gam gyi gnam sgo la /
NK013(pa)010:682: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u phata /
NK013(pa)010:684: kho bo mi g.yo ba ljang nag ral gri dang sdigs mdzub can gcig gis sgo bsrung bar gyur /
NK013(pa)010:687: sgrib pa phral ba gnyis kyi /
NK013(pa)010:689: slob dpon zhe sdang rdo rje gsal bas /
NK013(pa)010:690: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK013(pa)010:691: ha la ha la ha la h'u /
NK013(pa)010:693: sprul pa'i khro tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa spros /
NK013(pa)010:694: bdud bgegs log par 'dren pa'i tshogs thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:695: bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)010:696: 'dir 'dus pa'i slob bu rnams la gnod cing 'tshe
NK013(pa)010:697: ba'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par dengs
NK013(pa)010:699: h'u bzhi pa'i sngags lan gsum brjod cing gu gul gyi bdug /
NK013(pa)010:702: slob dpon gyi lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga
NK013(pa)010:703: la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du h'u
NK013(pa)010:704: s+w+aa +aam h+aam / g.yon gyi sor mo lnga zla
NK013(pa)010:705: ba'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du m+aum l+aam m+aam
NK013(pa)010:706: p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan pa rnams rigs lnga yab
NK013(pa)010:707: yum bcur gyur par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:713: zhes phyag rgya bsdams pas rigs lnga yab yum mnyam par sbyor bar bsam /
NK013(pa)010:714: bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)010:715: slob bu 'di rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:716: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:718: lta ba dman pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:719: chos kyis phongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:720: bag chags ngan pa'i sgrib pa la sogs te sgrib
NK013(pa)010:721: pa'i phung po ji snyed pa thams cad phyag rgya'i
NK013(pa)010:724: zhes pa'i sngags mang du brjod cing phyag rgya sprul pas /
NK013(pa)010:725: rigs lnga'i sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK013(pa)010:726: zer 'phros pas slob bu'i sgrib pa mtha' dag bsregs
NK013(pa)010:727: shing sbyangs / dung khang gi khro bo gnyis kyang
NK013(pa)010:728: zhu lugs su thim pa'i rkyen gyis bu'i lus kyang
NK013(pa)010:729: 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung gser zhun ma lta
NK013(pa)010:731: brgyad pa lhar brlab pa la /
NK013(pa)010:733: bskur brlab go bgo lus bsrung bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:734: h'u zhes brjod pas de nyid h'u yig dkar po gcig tu gyur /
NK013(pa)010:737: 'phro 'dus rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur /
NK013(pa)010:740: 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje sems
NK013(pa)010:741: dpa' sku mdog dkar po rdor dril 'dzin pa rgyan
NK013(pa)010:742: dang cha lugs thams cad rdzogs par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)010:743: so so'i phyag rgya slob ma'i mgo bo'i gnas lnga bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:744: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aa t+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:751: +aahmh'u zhes brjod cing rdo rje gnas gsum du gtugs pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK013(pa)010:752: slar yang rdo rje rtse lnga'i rgya bcings pa gnas gsum du bzhag /
NK013(pa)010:753: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:757: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su dpral bar sku rdo
NK013(pa)010:758: rje rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa
NK013(pa)010:759: 'dzin pa / mgrin par gsung rdo rje snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma +aahs mtshan pa 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)010:760: snying gar thugs rdo rje mi bskyod pa mthing ga
NK013(pa)010:761: rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa 'dzin pa rnams kyis
NK013(pa)010:763: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya spyi bor bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:764: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK013(pa)010:766: mdzub mo g.yas su trum la sa khro bo rdo
NK013(pa)010:767: rje gnod sbyin nag po phyag gnyis kyis mche ba
NK013(pa)010:768: dang sdigs mdzub / g.yon du las khro bo mi
NK013(pa)010:769: 'chi thab sbyor dmar po rgya gram dang sdigs mdzub
NK013(pa)010:776: spyi bo rnams su rim par mdzub mo gnyis bsnol ba reg pas /
NK013(pa)010:777: gnas de dang der khro bo gnyis po zung re
NK013(pa)010:778: zhabs bsnol nas zhal phyir gzigs te bsrung ba'i las
NK013(pa)010:779: mdzad pa'i thugs ka nas rdo rje'i lu gu rgyud
NK013(pa)010:780: byug pas bsrungs shing brtan par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)010:781: dgu pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:783: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK013(pa)010:784: a la la ste mnyes par mdzod //
NK013(pa)010:785: a la la ste dam tshig skong //
NK013(pa)010:786: a la la ste dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)010:787: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba //
NK013(pa)010:788: mi phyed rdo rje'i sku rang bzhin //
NK013(pa)010:789: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK013(pa)010:790: rdo rje'i sku ru mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)010:792: slob dpon gyis bdud rtsi la /
NK013(pa)010:793: +aahmh'u zhes brjod pas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rdo
NK013(pa)010:794: rje gsum gyi rang bzhin 'bru gsum gyi rnam par
NK013(pa)010:795: gsal btab la / badz+ra a mri tam a d+hi
NK013(pa)010:796: tish+tha mam h'u h+r+aihth+aah zhes lan gsum gyis byin gyis
NK013(pa)010:797: brlabs pa bla ma'i phyag g.yas rdo rje dang bcas
NK013(pa)010:798: pa'i srin lag gis blangs nas /
NK013(pa)010:799: zhes slob ma'i dpral bar thig le byas pas /
NK013(pa)010:800: dpral bar dkar pos mtshan par bsam /
NK013(pa)010:801: de las 'od zer dkar po 'phros de bzhin gshegs
NK013(pa)010:802: pa thams cad kyi sku'i byin rlabs bsdus nas la
NK013(pa)010:804: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:805: zhes byin gyis brlabs pas sku'i dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK013(pa)010:807: dpal ldan rdo rje gsung 'chang ba //
NK013(pa)010:808: mi phyed rdo rje gsung rang bzhin //
NK013(pa)010:809: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK013(pa)010:810: rdo rje'i gsung du mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)010:813: am zhes mgrin par thig le byas pas /
NK013(pa)010:815: de las 'od zer dmar po 'phros de bzhin gshegs
NK013(pa)010:816: pa thams cad kyi gsung gi byin rlabs bsdus nas
NK013(pa)010:818: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:819: zhes byin gyis brlabs pas gsung gi dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK013(pa)010:821: dpal ldan rdo rje thugs 'chang ba //
NK013(pa)010:822: mi phyed rdo rje thugs rang bzhin //
NK013(pa)010:823: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK013(pa)010:824: rdo rje'i thugs su mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)010:826: h'u zhes snying gar thig le byas pas h'u mthing gar bsam /
NK013(pa)010:827: de las 'od zer mthing ga 'phros de bzhin gshegs
NK013(pa)010:828: pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi byin rlabs bsdus nas
NK013(pa)010:829: h'u la thim par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:830: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:831: zhes byin gyis brlabs pas thugs kyi dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK013(pa)010:832: bcu pa dam tshig dbab pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:833: rdo rje snying gar bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:834: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK013(pa)010:835: dam nyams ma 'dres med pa la //
NK013(pa)010:836: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK013(pa)010:837: theg pa chen po ston byed pa //
NK013(pa)010:838: de la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK013(pa)010:839: sku gsung thugs la rtag gnas shing //
NK013(pa)010:840: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK013(pa)010:842: bcu gcig pa chu nan bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:843: dung zhal du tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu las sngags kyi bsang /
NK013(pa)010:845: stong pa'i ngang las h'u las khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin du gyur /
NK013(pa)010:846: e h+ye his rang 'dra'i ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK013(pa)010:850: lha 'od du zhu ba chu'i rdul phra rab tu bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:851: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK013(pa)010:852: dam tshig nyams na sreg par byed //
NK013(pa)010:853: rdo rje khro bo chen por 'gyur //
NK013(pa)010:854: rdo rje'i chu 'di btung bar gyis //
NK013(pa)010:856: ces rdo rjes lce la lan gsum bzhag cing nyes dmigs kyi sgo nas chu nan bya /
NK013(pa)010:857: de nas phan yon gyi sgo nas chu nan bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:859: stong pa'i ngang las h'u las rdo rje h'u gis
NK013(pa)010:860: mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje sems
NK013(pa)010:861: dpa'i skur bskyed la sngar ltar /
NK013(pa)010:862: e h+ye his rang 'ad+r+aa ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK013(pa)010:866: lha zhu ba las byung ba'i bdud rtsir bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:867: de lta bas na bu khyod kyis //
NK013(pa)010:868: dam tshig 'di dag bsrung bar gyis //
NK013(pa)010:869: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub pas //
NK013(pa)010:870: rdo rje'i bdud rtsi'i chu 'thungs shig /
NK013(pa)010:871: badz+ra u da ka h'u phata /
NK013(pa)010:872: ces lan gsum byin rjes 'di ltar brjod de /
NK013(pa)010:873: de ltar bdud rtsi'i chu 'di bzhag pa lce la
NK013(pa)010:874: bzhag kyang babs pa snying gi dkyil du babs nas
NK013(pa)010:875: / gal te dam tshig ma bsrung na //
NK013(pa)010:876: chu de rdo rje gnod sbyin zhes bya ba lcags
NK013(pa)010:877: kyi sdig pa mgo dgu par gyur nas snying khrag
NK013(pa)010:878: zho bzhin 'jib pas tshe thung zhing nad mang ba
NK013(pa)010:879: dang / tshe phyi mar dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag par 'gyur ro //
NK013(pa)010:880: dam tshig bsrungs na chu de rdo rje sems dpar gyur nas de rtag tu byin gyis brlab cing /
NK013(pa)010:882: smon brgyad du gyur nas nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi gdon stong phrag brgyad cus mi tshugs pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:883: phyi mar bla na med pa'i byang chub thob nas
NK013(pa)010:884: sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK013(pa)010:885: 'das pa'i gnas su 'dren pa'i ded dpon byed par
NK013(pa)010:887: bcu gnyis pa dam tshig bsgrag pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:888: bla ma'i phyag g.yas rdo rje dang bcas pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:889: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyis //
NK013(pa)010:890: rtag tu dogs pa med gyis la /
NK013(pa)010:892: / 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan spyod //
NK013(pa)010:893: gzhan yang stong khams thams cad na //
NK013(pa)010:894: shes rab dbyings dang 'dod yon gzhan //
NK013(pa)010:895: rab 'bring tha ma thams cad spyod //
NK013(pa)010:896: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK013(pa)010:897: skye bo gang zhig dam la gnod //
NK013(pa)010:898: brtul zhugs can gyis de drongs la //
NK013(pa)010:899: khrag chen snying las btung bar gyis /
NK013(pa)010:901: / 'di la mi bya cung zad med //
NK013(pa)010:902: sems nyid theg par rab nges na //
NK013(pa)010:903: nyon mongs 'dod lnga kun spyad kyang //
NK013(pa)010:905: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK013(pa)010:906: bya dang mi bya cung zad med //
NK013(pa)010:908: bcu gsum pa rin chen dor ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:909: sngar gtad pa'i me tog thal sbyar gyis bzung ba
NK013(pa)010:910: slob dpon gyi lus gdod nas rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK013(pa)010:911: du bzhugs pa la 'dor bar gsungs kyang 'jug pa
NK013(pa)010:912: bde phyir man+dala gyi ra ba 'di nyid rigs lnga'i
NK013(pa)010:913: lhar bzhugs pa la dmigs te /
NK013(pa)010:914: me tog la sogs rin chen phreng //
NK013(pa)010:915: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK013(pa)010:916: thugs rjes bzung bar dgongs nas kyang //
NK013(pa)010:917: gang yin de la 'bab gyur cig /
NK013(pa)010:918: pra t+aits+tsha badz+ra hoh zhes 'dor du bcug pas /
NK013(pa)010:919: dbus su babs na rdo rje'i rigs /
NK013(pa)010:924: de ltar rigs gang yin ngos zungs shig /
NK013(pa)010:926: pra t+ai grih+na t+wam i mam sa t+wa ma h+aa ba la tish+tha /
NK013(pa)010:928: bcu bzhi pa lha dbab pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:929: slob bu rnams lus gnad drang por bsrangs te rlung rang babs su bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:930: snying nang du chu nan gyi ye shes pa rdo
NK013(pa)010:931: rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po zhal phyag phyag
NK013(pa)010:932: mtshan yongs su rdzogs par gsal ba la shes pa
NK013(pa)010:933: skad cig kyang ma yengs par gyis shig /
NK013(pa)010:935: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgya bcas la /
NK013(pa)010:939: rdo rje sems dpa' chos sku las gzugs skur bzhengs par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:940: dbang phyug gis lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK013(pa)010:941: badz+ra sa t+wa e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma
NK013(pa)010:942: h+aa k+aa ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma
NK013(pa)010:943: ya s+t+wam / dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes brjod pas 'og
NK013(pa)010:944: min nas ye shes sems dpa'i rang bzhin rdo rje
NK013(pa)010:945: sems dpa'i sku che chung bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK013(pa)010:946: byon nas slob ma'i spyi bo'i steng gi nam mkhar
NK013(pa)010:948: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)010:949: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)010:950: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la babs //
NK013(pa)010:951: byin gyis rlob pa'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)010:952: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)010:953: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)010:955: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)010:956: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)010:957: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)010:958: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK013(pa)010:960: zhes brjod cing spos rol bya /
NK013(pa)010:961: de nas bla ma'i phyag g.yas rdo rje dang bcas pa slob ma'i snying gar bzhag la /
NK013(pa)010:963: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK013(pa)010:964: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK013(pa)010:965: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:966: bden pa chen pos byin gyi rlabs kyis byin phab
NK013(pa)010:967: pa'i ye shes pa de nyid tsit+ta'i dkyil du ye
NK013(pa)010:968: shes sems dpa'i rang bzhin du bzhugs nas 'jig rten
NK013(pa)010:969: 'di'i dge dgu dang smon brgyad du gyur te /
NK013(pa)010:970: phyi ma bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi rgyur gyur cig /
NK013(pa)010:971: gal te dam tshig nyams na rdo rje gnod sbyin
NK013(pa)010:972: du gyur nas srog rtsa'i khrag 'jib par gyur cig
NK013(pa)010:975: ces pas snying gi sgo phye la nam mkha' gang
NK013(pa)010:976: ba'i lha tshogs rnams slob ma'i sbyi bo nas zhugs
NK013(pa)010:977: pa snying ga'i rdo rje sems dpa' la sib sib
NK013(pa)010:978: thim par bsam zhing spos rol dang bcas te /
NK013(pa)010:980: zhes chu nan gyi lha dang gnyis med du gyur par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)010:981: bco lnga pa lha sgom par nan tan bya ba
NK013(pa)010:982: ni 'og tu dkyil 'khor gyi lha ngo bstan pa
NK013(pa)010:983: dang sbrel nas mdzad pa phyag len no //
NK013(pa)010:984: bcu drug pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:985: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas 'od zer thur ma 'dra ba byung ste /
NK013(pa)010:986: slob bu'i ma rig pa'i ling thog bsal bas dag
NK013(pa)010:987: pa ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan par mos la
NK013(pa)010:988: / de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni //
NK013(pa)010:989: dkyil 'khor dam pa blta bar bya //
NK013(pa)010:990: sangs rgyas gang gi rigs su 'khrungs //
NK013(pa)010:991: dngos grub mchog tu 'gyur bar bya //
NK013(pa)010:992: badz+ra tsak+shu pra we sha ya phata /
NK013(pa)010:993: ces mig dbye zhing gdong g.yogs dgrol /
NK013(pa)010:994: bcu bdun pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:995: dbang phyug gis phyag shing thogs te /
NK013(pa)010:998: spro na 'grel pa nyi seng mar gsungs pa ltar /
NK013(pa)010:1000: da ni dad pa rab skyed cig /
NK013(pa)010:1001: sangs rgyas gdung gi rigs su 'khrungs //
NK013(pa)010:1002: dam tshig mchog tu 'gyur ba yi //
NK013(pa)010:1003: rdo rje pad+mo rol mo'i mchog /
NK013(pa)010:1004: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlab //
NK013(pa)010:1005: dngos grub thams cad phun sum tshogs //
NK013(pa)010:1006: gsang sngags rnams ni sgrub par gyis //
NK013(pa)010:1008: de yang bsrung ba'i 'khor los mi phyed par bcings
NK013(pa)010:1009: pa'i nang du sna tshogs pad+ma'i lte ba la rdzogs
NK013(pa)010:1010: pa'i gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo
NK013(pa)010:1011: gsal ba la / ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK013(pa)010:1012: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK013(pa)010:1013: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK013(pa)010:1014: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa /
NK013(pa)010:1015: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK013(pa)010:1016: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad dang so so ma
NK013(pa)010:1017: yin ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu
NK013(pa)010:1018: 'khyil ba / ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK013(pa)010:1019: ye shes rin po che'i dbyibs dang kha dog la
NK013(pa)010:1020: sogs pa rnam pa tha dad pa'i bye brag dang
NK013(pa)010:1024: ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyi phreng ba dang /
NK013(pa)010:1031: reg bya sna tshogs kyis phyogs bcur 'khrigs par rang
NK013(pa)010:1032: byung la mi sgrib par gsal ba'i rgyan bsam gyis
NK013(pa)010:1034: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can /
NK013(pa)010:1035: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa /
NK013(pa)010:1036: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa na /
NK013(pa)010:1038: rigs lnga'i gnas su mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK013(pa)010:1039: stobs glang po che'i khri dang /
NK013(pa)010:1042: thogs pa med pa nam mkha' lding gi khri dang /
NK013(pa)010:1043: rigs lnga dang bya byed kyi gnas su re ba yid bzhin du skong ba rin po che'i gdan /
NK013(pa)010:1044: rigs lnga bya byed sems dpa' rnams kyi gnas su
NK013(pa)010:1045: gos pa med pa pad+ma'i gdan la rang bzhin gyi
NK013(pa)010:1047: thub pa drug la pad rkyang dang /
NK013(pa)010:1048: mthar byed kyi gnas su nyi ma'i gdan re re ste /
NK013(pa)010:1049: de rnams ni rten gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK013(pa)010:1051: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi gdan la rnam par shes
NK013(pa)010:1052: pa gnas su dag pa thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid
NK013(pa)010:1053: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog mthing
NK013(pa)010:1054: ga mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi
NK013(pa)010:1055: g.yas dang po rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin cing /
NK013(pa)010:1056: g.yon dang po dril bu dkur brten pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK013(pa)010:1057: bar pa gnyis 'khor lo dang rin po che /
NK013(pa)010:1058: tha ma gnyis kyis pad+ma dang ral gri 'dzin pa dbu skra ral pa'i thor tshugs can /
NK013(pa)010:1059: zhabs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'i
NK013(pa)010:1060: pang du 'byung ba nam mkha'i khams gnas su dag
NK013(pa)010:1061: pa yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma sngon
NK013(pa)010:1062: mo phyag g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab kyi mgul
NK013(pa)010:1063: nas 'khyud cing / g.yon rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin
NK013(pa)010:1064: pa brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba
NK013(pa)010:1065: nas 'khyud cing / / gnyis ka'ang dar gyi chas
NK013(pa)010:1066: gos lnga dang rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis brgyan
NK013(pa)010:1067: pa zhi ba'i tshul dgus brjid cing 'od zer kha
NK013(pa)010:1068: dog drug re re yang bye ba phrag drug drug
NK013(pa)010:1069: tu 'phro zhing 'bar ba'i klong na bde stong gnyis
NK013(pa)010:1070: su med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK013(pa)010:1071: rtsibs bzhi'i shar gyi rtsibs la gzugs phung dang 'byung
NK013(pa)010:1072: ba sa'i khams gnas su dag pa sku rdo rje'i
NK013(pa)010:1073: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad dang
NK013(pa)010:1075: lho'i rtsibs la tshor phung dang 'byung ba chu'i khams
NK013(pa)010:1076: gnas su dag pa yon tan rdo rje'i bdag nyid
NK013(pa)010:1077: bcom ldan 'das rin chen 'byung ldan dang yum m+aa
NK013(pa)010:1078: ma k+ai / nub kyi rtsibs la 'du shes dang
NK013(pa)010:1079: 'byung ba me'i khams gnas su dag pa gsung rdo
NK013(pa)010:1080: rje'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das snang ba mtha' yas
NK013(pa)010:1082: byang gi rtsibs la 'du byed dang 'byung ba rlung
NK013(pa)010:1083: gi khams gnas su dag pa phrin las rdo rje'i
NK013(pa)010:1084: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das don yod grub pa dang
NK013(pa)010:1086: rtsibs mchan bzhi'i shar lhor mig shes dang yul gzugs rnam par dag pa sa snying yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1087: lho nub tu sna'i rnam shes dang yul dri gnas su dag pa nam snying yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1088: nub byang du lce'i rnam shes dang yul sgra gnas su dag pa spyan ras gzigs yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1089: byang shar du rna ba'i rnam shes dang yul ro gnas su dag pa phyag rdor yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1090: gru chad bzhi'i shar lhor mig dbang dang 'das pa'i dus gnas su dag pa byams pa yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1091: lho nub tu rna ba'i dbang po dang da ltar
NK013(pa)010:1092: gyi dus gnas su dag pa sgrib sel yab yum
NK013(pa)010:1093: / nub byang du sna dbang dang ma 'ongs pa'i dus gnas su dag pa kun bzang yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1094: byang shar du lce dbang dang ma nges pa'i dus gnas su dag pa 'jam dpal yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1095: khyams kyi shar nub gnyis su yid chos gnas su dag pa bya byed yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1096: khyams kyi shar lhor nga rgyal gnas su dag pa lha'i thub pa /
NK013(pa)010:1097: byang du phrag dog gnas su dag pa lha min gyi thub pa /
NK013(pa)010:1098: lhor 'dod chags gnas su dag pa mi'i thub pa /
NK013(pa)010:1099: nub byang du gti mug gnas su dag pa byol song gi thub pa /
NK013(pa)010:1100: lho nub tu ser sna gnas su dag pa yi dwags kyi thub pa /
NK013(pa)010:1101: byang shar du zhe sdang gnas su dag pa dmyal ba'i thub pa /
NK013(pa)010:1102: shar sgor reg pa dang rtag par lta ba gnas su dag pa gshin rje gshed yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1103: lho sgor reg bya dang chad par lta ba gnas su dag pa stobs chen yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1104: nub sgor reg byed dang bdag tu lta ba gnas su dag pa rta mgrin yab yum /
NK013(pa)010:1105: byang sgor reg shes dang mtshan mar lta ba gnas
NK013(pa)010:1106: su dag pa bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yab yum ste
NK013(pa)010:1107: de ltar na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba bzhi
NK013(pa)010:1108: bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor chen po /
NK013(pa)010:1109: rten dang brten par bcas pa thams cad mngon sum
NK013(pa)010:1110: bzhin du mjal bar gyur snyam du dga' ba dang
NK013(pa)010:1111: spro ba yang dag pa bskyed mdzod /
NK013(pa)010:1112: de'i nang nas kyang khyod kyi yi dam gyi lha ni 'di yin te /
NK013(pa)010:1113: de yang sngon me tog dbus su babs pa rnams
NK013(pa)010:1114: kyi yi dam gyi lha ni mi bskyod pa dang
NK013(pa)010:1118: de bzhin du shar du babs pa rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha ni rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK013(pa)010:1122: lho ru babs pa rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha ni rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK013(pa)010:1126: nub tu babs pa rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha ni snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK013(pa)010:1130: byang du babs pa rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha ni don yod grub pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:1134: de ltar na dus rtag tu lha de dang de'i
NK013(pa)010:1135: mngon rtogs sgom pa dang sngags bzla ba la brtson
NK013(pa)010:1137: de nas skabs 'dir rigs gang la babs pa'i gsang mtshan gdags par bya ste /
NK013(pa)010:1152: rdo rje bee ro tsa na rtsal /
NK013(pa)010:1158: rdo rje yon tan gter 'byung rtsal /
NK013(pa)010:1160: rdo rje rin chen snying po rtsal /
NK013(pa)010:1169: rdo rje ma chags pad+ma rtsal /
NK013(pa)010:1184: rigs dang mthun pa'i ming gdags te /
NK013(pa)010:1185: de lta bu'i ming de nyid ma brjed par gyis shig /
NK013(pa)010:1186: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su rigs de dang der mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i tshe /
NK013(pa)010:1189: sa steng gsum du grags par 'gyur zhing sems can gyi don byed pa dang /
NK013(pa)010:1190: khyad par du zhe sdang can la sogs pa'i gdul bya 'dul bar 'gyur ro //
NK013(pa)010:1192: de nas khe nyen bshad pa'i sgo nas lha sgom par gdams pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:1193: skal ba mnyan pa'i ye shes de //
NK013(pa)010:1194: gnyer na nye bar 'byung ba yi //
NK013(pa)010:1195: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK013(pa)010:1196: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK013(pa)010:1197: lha spangs dge spyad don med pas //
NK013(pa)010:1198: gang gis phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK013(pa)010:1199: nyon mongs ngan song gnas su skye //
NK013(pa)010:1201: bla med 'gro ba'i rgyun yang chad //
NK013(pa)010:1202: rigs chad nyid du ltung bar 'gyur //
NK013(pa)010:1203: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)010:1205: gcig dang du ma yongs bral bas //
NK013(pa)010:1208: bco brgyad pa yon 'bul ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:1210: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK013(pa)010:1211: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK013(pa)010:1212: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK013(pa)010:1214: zhes gsungs pas lus dang longs spyod thams cad ltos
NK013(pa)010:1215: med du phul ba'i mos pas de mtshon byed du
NK013(pa)010:1216: man+dala 'bul / de ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i yon tan la bzhi las /
NK013(pa)010:1217: dang po dkyil 'khor 'dir zhugs pas dkyil 'khor thams cad du zhugs par 'gyur pa'i yon tan ni /
NK013(pa)010:1219: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bar legs zhugs pas //
NK013(pa)010:1220: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK013(pa)010:1221: dkyil 'khor kun tu zhugs pa yin //
NK013(pa)010:1223: gnyis pa mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs pas rang
NK013(pa)010:1224: bzhin 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa dang skal
NK013(pa)010:1225: ba mnyam par 'gyur pa'i yon tan ni /
NK013(pa)010:1227: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i /
NK013(pa)010:1229: / 'khor lo mngon du mthong ba yi //
NK013(pa)010:1230: bsod nams brtag pa gang yin pa //
NK013(pa)010:1231: phyis byas pa yang de bzhin no //
NK013(pa)010:1233: gsum pa mos pa skyes pa tsam gyis rgyal ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur ba'i yon tan ni /
NK013(pa)010:1235: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK013(pa)010:1236: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)010:1237: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK013(pa)010:1238: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yis //
NK013(pa)010:1239: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)010:1241: bzhi pa dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas dam tshig ma
NK013(pa)010:1242: nyams na mchog thun gyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur
NK013(pa)010:1245: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rigs nges shing //
NK013(pa)010:1246: gdon rnams bzlog cing ngan song spong //
NK013(pa)010:1247: longs spyod 'du ba rnam gnyis dang //
NK013(pa)010:1248: ye shes spyan gyi gzhi ru nges //
NK013(pa)010:1249: de la sogs pa bsam yas mchog /
NK013(pa)010:1251: de dag ni dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga'o //
NK013(pa)010:1252: gnyis pa zhugs pa la mngon par dbang bskur ba'i cho ga ni /
NK013(pa)010:1254: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs pas //
NK013(pa)010:1255: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK013(pa)010:1256: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK013(pa)010:1257: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK013(pa)010:1259: slob ma dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK013(pa)010:1260: rang gzhan gyi don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga /
NK013(pa)010:1261: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la gsang ba
NK013(pa)010:1262: zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba'i rim pa dang gsum
NK013(pa)010:1263: / dang po phan dbang bskur ba la /
NK013(pa)010:1267: slob ma rnams kyis bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha la phyag sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)010:1268: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK013(pa)010:1269: brtse bar dgongs te bdag la yang //
NK013(pa)010:1270: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid //
NK013(pa)010:1271: de ring rab tu gsal bar mdzod //
NK013(pa)010:1272: ces lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK013(pa)010:1273: de nas 'grel pa nyi seng mar gsungs pa ltar /
NK013(pa)010:1274: slob ma dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgo'i nang rol du
NK013(pa)010:1275: dbang stegs pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i steng du rdo
NK013(pa)010:1276: rje mi bskyod pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i rnam
NK013(pa)010:1278: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)010:1279: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK013(pa)010:1280: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK013(pa)010:1281: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK013(pa)010:1283: spos dang rol mor bcas pas dkyil 'khor la bskor zhing dbang phyug gis dkyil 'khor gyis lha la /
NK013(pa)010:1284: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK013(pa)010:1285: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK013(pa)010:1286: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK013(pa)010:1287: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)010:1289: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgyas /
NK013(pa)010:1290: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad
NK013(pa)010:1291: mdun gyi nam mkhar sprin phung gtibs pa bzhin du
NK013(pa)010:1292: sad nas bzhugs par mos la me tog dang bcas
NK013(pa)010:1294: hoh phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK013(pa)010:1295: bdag rdo rje slob dpon 'di zhes bya bas slob
NK013(pa)010:1296: bu 'di rnams la sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dbang bskur
NK013(pa)010:1297: bas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag la
NK013(pa)010:1301: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)010:1303: rdo rje shugs kyis bsgral nas kyang //
NK013(pa)010:1304: byin rlabs dam pa nod par bya'o //
NK013(pa)010:1305: zhes brjod cing dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su 'dug par
NK013(pa)010:1306: mos la rang nyid dbang khri la 'dug par bya'o
NK013(pa)010:1309: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK013(pa)010:1310: rim las skyon yon brgyad ces bya //
NK013(pa)010:1311: zhes pa ltar dbang thams cad la don brgyad brgyad du bsdus nas gsungs pa las /
NK013(pa)010:1312: dbang re re la yang drug pa yan chad gseb tshags su 'byung bar shes par bya la /
NK013(pa)010:1314: snying po lnga dang dbu rgyan dang /
NK013(pa)010:1315: bum pa cod pan phreng ba ste //
NK013(pa)010:1316: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs phyag rgya //
NK013(pa)010:1317: bza' btung dbang rnams rim bzhin bskur //
NK013(pa)010:1318: zhes pa'i sdoms ltar phan dbang bcu'i dang po snying po lnga'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:1319: dbang rdzas rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan mdun du bshams la /
NK013(pa)010:1323: dbang rdzas mi dmigs par stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK013(pa)010:1324: stong pa'i ngang las pad nyi zla ba'i gdan la
NK013(pa)010:1325: +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa las so so'i phyag mtshan sa bon
NK013(pa)010:1326: gyis mtshan pa 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las
NK013(pa)010:1327: rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)010:1328: snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)010:1329: mi bskyod pa mthing ga rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)010:1330: rin 'byung ser po rin chen 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)010:1331: don grub ljang gu ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)010:1332: lnga ka'ang g.yon dril bu 'dzin cing rdzogs pa'i skyil
NK013(pa)010:1333: mo krung gis bzhugs pa rang rang gi yum dang
NK013(pa)010:1335: +aa dar+sha sogs rang rigs bdag por byas pa'i sngags lnga tshan lngas dbang bskur /
NK013(pa)010:1336: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK013(pa)010:1340: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par bya /
NK013(pa)010:1341: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyi mchod nas /
NK013(pa)010:1342: yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i rjes chags kyis zhu
NK013(pa)010:1343: ba las byung ba'i dbang rdzas rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan
NK013(pa)010:1344: sa bon gyis mtshan par gyur /
NK013(pa)010:1345: de nas dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od
NK013(pa)010:1346: zer 'phros pa slob ma'i dpral bar phog pa'i rkyen
NK013(pa)010:1347: gyis zla ba'i gdan la yig dkar pos mtshan par
NK013(pa)010:1351: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rnam
NK013(pa)010:1352: snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab par
NK013(pa)010:1353: gyur / de nas dbang rdzas 'khor lo dpral bar
NK013(pa)010:1354: bzhag pa bdud rtsi dri chen gyi khams la thim
NK013(pa)010:1355: pas sku rdo rje'i dbang thob par mos la //
NK013(pa)010:1356: bde gshegs sku yi ngo bo las //
NK013(pa)010:1357: mi shigs rdo rje rgyal ba'i gtso //
NK013(pa)010:1358: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yis //
NK013(pa)010:1359: rdo rje sku yi ngo bor shog /
NK013(pa)010:1360: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:1361: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer
NK013(pa)010:1362: 'phros pa slob ma'i mgrin par phog pa'i rkyen gyis
NK013(pa)010:1363: pad+ma'i gdan la +aam yig dmar pos mtshan par gyur
NK013(pa)010:1367: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las snang
NK013(pa)010:1368: mtha' dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pas rgyas btab par gyur
NK013(pa)010:1369: / de nas dbang rdzas pad+ma mgrin par bzhag pa
NK013(pa)010:1370: dmar cha'i khams la thim pas gsung rdo rje'i dbang
NK013(pa)010:1373: bde gshegs gsung gi ngo bo las //
NK013(pa)010:1374: mi shigs rdo rje chos kyi dbyings //
NK013(pa)010:1375: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yis //
NK013(pa)010:1376: rdo rje gsung gi ngo bor shog /
NK013(pa)010:1377: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:1378: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer
NK013(pa)010:1379: 'phros pa slob ma'i snying gar phog pa'i rkyen gyis
NK013(pa)010:1380: nyi ma'i gdan la h+aum yig mthing gas mtshan par
NK013(pa)010:1383: 'phro 'dus rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan par gyur /
NK013(pa)010:1384: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las mi
NK013(pa)010:1385: bskyod pa mthing ga rdo rje 'dzin pas rgyas btab
NK013(pa)010:1386: par gyur / de nas dbang rdzas rdo rje snying
NK013(pa)010:1387: gar bzhag pa dkar cha'i khams la thim pas thugs
NK013(pa)010:1388: rdo rje'i dbang thob par mos la /
NK013(pa)010:1390: bde gshegs thugs kyi ngo bo las //
NK013(pa)010:1391: mi shegs rdo rje thugs kyi thugs //
NK013(pa)010:1392: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yin //
NK013(pa)010:1393: rdo rje thugs kyi ngo bor shog /
NK013(pa)010:1394: sarba ta th+aa ga ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:1395: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer
NK013(pa)010:1396: 'phros pa slob ma'i lte ba'i g.yas su phog pa'i
NK013(pa)010:1397: rkyen gyis zla ba'i gdan la s+w+aa yig ser pos
NK013(pa)010:1398: mtshan par gyur / s+pha ra na phata /
NK013(pa)010:1400: 'phros 'dus rin po che s+w+aas mtshan par gyur /
NK013(pa)010:1401: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rin
NK013(pa)010:1402: 'byung ser po rin chen 'dzin pas rgyas btab par
NK013(pa)010:1403: gyur / de nas dbang rdzas rin po che lte
NK013(pa)010:1404: ba'i g.yas su bzhag pa sha chen gyi khams la
NK013(pa)010:1405: thim pas yon tan rdo rje'i dbang thob par mos
NK013(pa)010:1407: mi 'gyur ba yi zhing khams las //
NK013(pa)010:1408: ma skyes pa yi 'bras bur ldan //
NK013(pa)010:1409: ma bsags pa yi longs spyod 'byung //
NK013(pa)010:1410: cir yang 'gyur ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK013(pa)010:1411: rang dbang thabs kyis bsgyur bar shog /
NK013(pa)010:1412: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)010:1413: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer
NK013(pa)010:1414: 'phros pa slob ma'i lte ba'i g.yon du phog pa'i
NK013(pa)010:1415: rkyen gyis zla ba'i gdan la h+aa yig ljang gus
NK013(pa)010:1416: mtshan par gyur / s+pha ra na phata /
NK013(pa)010:1418: 'phro 'dus ral gri h+aas mtshan par gyur /
NK013(pa)010:1419: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las don
NK013(pa)010:1420: grub ljang gu ral gri 'dzin pas rgyas btab par
NK013(pa)010:1421: gyur / de nas dbang rdzas ral gri lte ba'i
NK013(pa)010:1422: g.yon du bzhag pa dri chu'i khams la thim pas
NK013(pa)010:1423: phrin las rdo rje'i dbang thob par mos la /
NK013(pa)010:1425: thabs dang shes gnyis med pa'i /
NK013(pa)010:1428: las dang dngos grub kun snang bas //
NK013(pa)010:1429: ma lus mnyam par sbyor bar shog /
NK013(pa)010:1430: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa
NK013(pa)010:1431: ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aa t+ma ko&a ham
