NK013(pa)010:2794: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)010:2795: rdzogs pa'i phyag rgya khyod las byung //
NK013(pa)010:2796: spangs nas rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsa //
NK013(pa)010:2797: dgug dang bsdam pa ma shes na //
NK013(pa)010:2798: rdo rje bskal pa mtha' klas par //
NK013(pa)010:2799: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK013(pa)010:2801: de nas slob ma dang gtad pa'i phyag rgya gnyis
NK013(pa)010:2802: phan tshun 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas
NK013(pa)010:2803: par byas rjes / slob ma dkyil 'khor gyi gtso
NK013(pa)010:2804: bo bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpar gsal ba'i
NK013(pa)010:2805: gnas lngar rgyal ba rigs lnga dang /
NK013(pa)010:2807: kha dang gsang ba'i phyi rnams su khro bo bzhi /
NK013(pa)010:2808: phyag rgya yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug mar gsal ba'i gnas lngar rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK013(pa)010:2809: yan lag bzhi la khro mo bzhi rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK013(pa)010:2817: yab kyi gsang gnas h+aum las ye shes kyi rdo
NK013(pa)010:2818: rje rtse mo lnga pa'i lte bar byang chub kyi
NK013(pa)010:2819: sems dkar por gnas pa'i bu ga phata kyis bkag
NK013(pa)010:2820: cing / rwa lnga la nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga /
NK013(pa)010:2821: yum gyi mkha' bam las pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma
NK013(pa)010:2822: bzhi pa'i lte bar nyi ma la rak+ta am dmar
NK013(pa)010:2823: por gnas pa'i ge sar la a /
NK013(pa)010:2824: dbus dang 'dab bzhir zla ba la gnas pa'i dpa' mo 'bru lngas mtshan par bsam la /
NK013(pa)010:2826: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK013(pa)010:2827: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK013(pa)010:2828: zhes sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te /
NK013(pa)010:2829: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis 'khyud sdom sprad nas /
NK013(pa)010:2830: snyoms par zhugs pas byang chub kyi sems 'khor lo
NK013(pa)010:2831: bzhir yas babs kyi rim par dga' ba bcu drug
NK013(pa)010:2832: gi 'gros kyis phyin pa las nyi zla zung 'brel
NK013(pa)010:2834: zla ba'i thig le re re bzhin ye shes lnga'i
NK013(pa)010:2835: nyams dang ldan pas dpe byad brgyad cu rdzogs shing
NK013(pa)010:2836: mngon shes drug kyang shar nas yum gyi rtsa kha
NK013(pa)010:2837: kha mu kha'i rtser nyi zla gnyis 'dres 'khyil ba
NK013(pa)010:2838: de nyid rdo rje nor bur bstim pa h'u zhes
NK013(pa)010:2839: gyen du ldog pa'i sbyor bas mas brtan gyi dga'
NK013(pa)010:2840: bzhi'i ye shes nyams su myong bar byas pa'i dga'
NK013(pa)010:2841: bzhi'i ye shes re re la'ang dga' ba bzhi bzhi
NK013(pa)010:2842: ste bcu drug gi dang po bzhis tshogs lam dang
NK013(pa)010:2843: / de nas re res sbyor mthong /
NK013(pa)010:2844: de nas dgus sgom lam sa dgu rdzogs te /
NK013(pa)010:2845: dga' ba bcu drug gi mtha' ma rang bzhin lhan
NK013(pa)010:2846: cig skyes pa'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes khyad
NK013(pa)010:2847: par can rgyud la skyes pa de'i tshe na snang
NK013(pa)010:2848: stong gi mtha' ma bsgribs par gsal bas kun tu
NK013(pa)010:2849: 'od dang / mi shigs pa'i dwangs mas lus thams
NK013(pa)010:2850: cad la khyab cing brtan pas 'khor ba'i skyon gyis
NK013(pa)010:2852: rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK013(pa)010:2853: 'khor rab 'byams su rang snang bas yi ge'i 'khor
NK013(pa)010:2855: mdor na thun mong dang khyad par gyi sa lam thams cad rdzogs par mos la /
NK013(pa)010:2857: rdo rje nyi ma thabs kyi rgya //
NK013(pa)010:2858: phung sogs phyag rgya'i tshogs dang ldan //
NK013(pa)010:2859: de zla bsil byed shes rab dngos //
NK013(pa)010:2860: dus gcig ro mnyam thig le che //
NK013(pa)010:2861: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan rdzogs shing //
NK013(pa)010:2862: zla ba'i ye shes lnga bcu drug /
NK013(pa)010:2863: dpe byad la sogs dpag tu med //
NK013(pa)010:2864: sems shes mngon par shes dang ldan //
NK013(pa)010:2866: gnas nas log pa thim pa'i sgra //
NK013(pa)010:2867: mtha' gnyis ma gos pad+ma can //
NK013(pa)010:2868: sprul pa'i gnas nas bkye ba yis //
NK013(pa)010:2869: bzhi bcu lnga sogs mtha' yas kun //
NK013(pa)010:2870: rang bzhin nyid las rang gsal ba //
NK013(pa)010:2871: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lor brjod //
NK013(pa)010:2872: d+harma k+aa ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK013(pa)010:2873: de ltar bskur tshig gis nyams su myong ba'i don
NK013(pa)010:2874: ngo sprad pas 'khor 'das mnyam nyid bde ba chen
NK013(pa)010:2875: po'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bsgyur te mchog tu mi
NK013(pa)010:2876: 'gyur ba de kho na nyid kyi don mngon du
NK013(pa)010:2880: phyogs bcu'i dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK013(pa)010:2881: khyod la bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur bas sgrib
NK013(pa)010:2882: gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa dag nas skye 'gag
NK013(pa)010:2883: gnyis su med pa zung 'jug don dam pa'i ye
NK013(pa)010:2884: shes mngon du rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK013(pa)010:2885: gyur cig / de ltar gsang ba b+ha ga'i dkyil
NK013(pa)010:2886: 'khor dang de kho na nyid sems kyi dkyil 'khor
NK013(pa)010:2887: du zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur bas thun mong ma
NK013(pa)010:2888: yin pa'i rdzogs rim rnams nyan sgom nus pa'i skal
NK013(pa)010:2889: ba can du byas pa yin no //
NK013(pa)010:2890: de nas dbang ma thob pa'i skyon dang /
NK013(pa)010:2893: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK013(pa)010:2894: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK013(pa)010:2895: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa rnams /
NK013(pa)010:2898: zhes dbang ma thob pa'i skyon dang /
NK013(pa)010:2899: dus 'di phyin cad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK013(pa)010:2900: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK013(pa)010:2901: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK013(pa)010:2902: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK013(pa)010:2903: zhes dbang thob pa'i phan yon gsungs te /
NK013(pa)010:2904: de bas na bskyed rdzogs kyi lam zab mo nyams
NK013(pa)010:2905: su len pa la dang por dbang nod pa shin
NK013(pa)010:2906: tu nas gces pa yin no //
NK013(pa)010:2907: des dbang bskur ba'i rim pa dngos song nas /
NK013(pa)010:2908: rjes kyi rim pa la bzhi yod pa'i /
NK013(pa)010:2909: dang po dbang rtags sbyin cing bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:2910: slob ma'i lag tu rdo rje gtad de gsor du bcug la /
NK013(pa)010:2911: sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK013(pa)010:2912: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK013(pa)010:2913: sangs rgyas kun tu rab bsgrub phyir //
NK013(pa)010:2914: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis longs //
NK013(pa)010:2915: dril bu gtad de dkrol du bcug la /
NK013(pa)010:2916: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK013(pa)010:2917: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen te //
NK013(pa)010:2919: chos la 'dod bzhin dbang bskur ro //
NK013(pa)010:2920: de nas slar yang rdor dril bsnol nas slob bu'i
NK013(pa)010:2921: lag pa g.yas g.yon du gtad de rdo rje gsor
NK013(pa)010:2922: zhing dril bu dkrol du bcug la /
NK013(pa)010:2923: badz+ra gan+de a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK013(pa)010:2927: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin skal ldan rig pa
NK013(pa)010:2928: 'dzin pa khyod la dbang rtags rdo rje dang dril
NK013(pa)010:2929: bu gtad de dbang bskur bas thabs dang shes rab
NK013(pa)010:2930: gnyis su med pas 'gro ba sems can gyi don
NK013(pa)010:2931: rgyun mi chad par byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK013(pa)010:2932: par gyur cig / de nas dbang phyug dbang khri
NK013(pa)010:2933: la 'dug pa'i zhabs g.yas pa la mgo bo gtug
NK013(pa)010:2934: par gyur cig / tu bcug ste / de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK013(pa)010:2935: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin pas //
NK013(pa)010:2936: nga yi ji skad bsgo ba bzhin //
NK013(pa)010:2937: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK013(pa)010:2939: gnyis pa bum chu blud cing smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK013(pa)010:2940: dbang phyug bzhengs te dbus kyi bum pa btegs la /
NK013(pa)010:2941: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK013(pa)010:2942: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK013(pa)010:2943: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK013(pa)010:2944: snying po lnga yi dbang bskur bas //
NK013(pa)010:2945: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK013(pa)010:2946: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK013(pa)010:2947: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK013(pa)010:2948: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK013(pa)010:2951: zhes dbang rnams brtan par bya /
NK013(pa)010:2952: gong ltar bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)010:2953: bdag rdo rje slob dpon che ge mos che ge
NK013(pa)010:2954: mo la sogs pa'i slob bu rnams la sgyu 'phrul
NK013(pa)010:2956: dus 'di phyin chad ngan song gsum la sogs pa'i
NK013(pa)010:2957: sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral nas mtho ris kyi
NK013(pa)010:2958: bde ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan te /
NK013(pa)010:2959: de las kyang rgyal ba'i sras rigs phun sum tshogs
NK013(pa)010:2960: pa'i sras su nges par dbang gi 'bras bu ma
NK013(pa)010:2961: lus pa la dbang thob nas srid pa'i sems can
NK013(pa)010:2962: mtha' dag gi don yongs su rdzogs par byed par
NK013(pa)010:2963: gyur cig / yul phyogs 'di la sogs te rgyal
NK013(pa)010:2964: khams thams cad du dus kyi 'khrug pa zhi bar
NK013(pa)010:2965: gyur cig / gyur cig / mtshon gyi bskal pa nyams par gyur cig /
NK013(pa)010:2966: mi nad phyugs nad thams cad rgyun chad par gyur cig /
NK013(pa)010:2968: lo phyugs rtag tu legs te sems can thams cad
NK013(pa)010:2969: bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan
NK013(pa)010:2970: par gyur cig / gsum pa dbang phyug gi dbang bsab cing slob bu'i lus bslu ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:2971: dbang phyug kun tu bzang por gsal ba'i thugs ka'i
NK013(pa)010:2972: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas dbang rdzas kyi rab
NK013(pa)010:2973: gnas kyi lha rnams gsal btab pa las /
NK013(pa)010:2974: slar yang h+aum zhes brjod cing bskur gnas rnams su
NK013(pa)010:2975: dbang rdzas rnams gtugs pas lha rnams 'od du zhu
NK013(pa)010:2976: ba so so'i mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la thim /
NK013(pa)010:2977: slar yang thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK013(pa)010:2978: mdun gyi nam mkhar dpang po'i tshul du bzhugs pa'i
NK013(pa)010:2979: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad
NK013(pa)010:2980: 'od du zhu nas dbang phyug la thim pas sngar
NK013(pa)010:2981: bas kyang nus pa cher skyes shing gzi 'od 'bar
NK013(pa)010:2982: bar bsam mo // de nas slob bu rnams kyis
NK013(pa)010:2983: phyag sngon du 'gro bas ci 'byor ba'i dngos pos
NK013(pa)010:2986: gnyis med rgyal ba'i mchog la rab gnas shing //
NK013(pa)010:2987: sku gsung thugs kyi rol pa cir ston pa'i //
NK013(pa)010:2988: bla med sman pa'i rgyal po bzhugs su gsol //
NK013(pa)010:2989: zang zing rdzas kyi dgos pas ma brel kyang //
NK013(pa)010:2990: bdag 'dzin sdug bsngal rtog pas bcings pa yi /
NK013(pa)010:2992: / 'khor ba'i 'dam rdzab klong nas drangs ba'i phyir /
NK013(pa)010:2994: / 'byor pas dmigs pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)010:2996: bzhi pa gtang rag gis mchod cing yon dbul ba ni /
NK013(pa)010:2997: slob bu'i gtso bos ka p+aa la mtshan ldan bdud
NK013(pa)010:2998: rtsis bkang ba mar chol dang bcas pa btegs la
NK013(pa)010:2999: / khyod ni ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi dpal //
NK013(pa)010:3000: dpal gyi phyag rgya mang po thob pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)010:3001: dus gsum kun tu sangs rgyas yin pa'i rtags //
NK013(pa)010:3002: rdo rje che mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)010:3003: ces dbang phyug gi zhal du drang zhing ci 'byor ba'i yon dbul /
NK013(pa)010:3004: rjes dam tshig khas blang ba dang /
NK013(pa)010:3006: dge ba bsngo zhing shis pa brjod pas kyang mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK013(pa)010:3007: rjes kyi cho ga rnams kyang sgrub dkyil bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK013(pa)010:3008: mchog tu gsang ba gdod ma'i gnas lugs gang /
NK013(pa)010:3010: / 'khrul med mngon sum gsal ba snying po'i bcud //
NK013(pa)010:3011: rgyal kun dgongs pa'i zhe phugs de kho na //
NK013(pa)010:3012: ji bzhin nyid du ston byed nges pa'i lam //
NK013(pa)010:3013: zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dkyil 'khor du //
NK013(pa)010:3014: skal ldan smin par byed pa'i thabs kyi sgo //
NK013(pa)010:3015: phan nus zab mo'i dbang gi cho ga 'di //
NK013(pa)010:3016: blo gsal snying gi gdung ba sel phyir spel //
NK013(pa)010:3017: yig rnying rnams la rkang pas 'jug 'dod kyang /
NK013(pa)010:3019: / 'dab chags rings pa'i bgrod pa nam mkha' la //
NK013(pa)010:3020: byed pa chos nyid yin phyir mdo sgyu gnyis //
NK013(pa)010:3021: ma 'dres 'byed pa phyogs 'di'i khyad chos yin //
NK013(pa)010:3022: gal te nyes bshad nongs pa'i cha mchis na /
NK013(pa)010:3024: / 'phags dang dam pa'i tshogs kyis bzod mdzad rigs /
NK013(pa)010:3026: / 'dir 'bad dge bas lus can 'gro ba kun //
NK013(pa)010:3027: rnam grol byang chub thob pa'i rgyur gyur cig /
NK013(pa)010:3028: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba 'bring po'i dbang gi
NK013(pa)010:3029: cho ga dkyil 'khor rgya mtshor 'jug pa'i gru chen
NK013(pa)010:3030: zhes bya ba 'di ni rang gzhan mang po la
NK013(pa)010:3031: phan 'dod dang / rigs kyi gcung 'gyur med yid
NK013(pa)010:3032: bzhin legs par grub pa'i gsung gis kyang bskul ma
NK013(pa)010:3033: btab par brten dus gsum rgyal ba'i spyi gzugs skyabs
NK013(pa)010:3034: mgon bla ma gter chen chos kyi rgyal po mched
NK013(pa)010:3035: kyi zhabs rdul spyi bos len pa smyos ban pad+ma
NK013(pa)010:3036: 'gyur med rgya mtsho mi pham rnam rgyal rdo rjes
NK013(pa)010:3037: rang lo nyer gcig pa mi zad pa'i lo khrums
NK013(pa)010:3038: zla'i dmar phyogs kyi tshes dge bar 'og min o
NK013(pa)010:3039: rgyan smin grol gling gi bla brang chos 'khor lhun
